channel.description:
http://usenet.eatddos.info/tracker/
thx to mepholic for da deal on vps and thx to c|p for subdomain!!
If you have any requests on games, software etc that you think is simply too slow for public torrents tell me and i'll put them there for your downloading convenience. You may upload ur own shit when you register as well!
EDIT: I am now taking donations. 100% of the money donated will go to the current vps and possibly future seedboxes to further enhance your downloading experience. Any amount is fine, however it would be optimal to end up around at least $50/month, that would mean i could pay for 2 seedboxes + the current server for seeds, hence download speeds would increase vastly.
Just click the "Donate" paypal-button on website to send a donation :)
